  "productPropertyListJson": "[{\"attr_name\":\"Portable Fan & Cool Fan\",\"attr_value\":\"If you're looking for something practical that's ideal for travel, outdoor or beach use then this little turbo fan with strong breeze should do meet you. Portable handheld fan has a high-speed turbo mode, a long-lasting working time, 5 speeds, and remaining battery LED display. Mini size the length is only 6.24in and weight is 7.12oz that easy carry or put in your trouser pocket.\"},{\"attr_name\":\"Little and Powerful\",\"attr_value\":\"This turbo personal handheld fan is a powerful and portable way to stay cool.small portable fan has 5 wind speed gears or 01-100 high speed wind gear,which the higher the setting wind gear and the cool wind is more strong and powerful.The maximum wind speed of up to 8 m/s. 15000RPM.You can choose wind speed of on any speed simply by pressing and holding,meeting your various wind power needs in any outdoor activities.\"},{\"attr_name\":\"Fast Charging and Long Battery Life\",\"attr_value\":\"Handheld turbo cool fan,which comes equipped with a 4000mAh rechargeable battery and LED display to show what wind speed it is running at and the number percentage show the battery charge left.This handheld Personal Fan has 5 blades and is rechargeable via the supplied USB-C cable. Powerful handheld fan takes about 3.30 hours to fully charge but using time it will last up to 18 hours depending on which degree of speed is selected.So it would last almost a day\"},{\"attr_name\":\"Outdoor and Companion\",\"attr_value\":\"Travel portable fan is a great companion for summer days.Handheld fan is perfect for so many occasions from outdoor activities,hiking,camping,sports activities,festivals, days out, holidays to picnics, barbecues to beach,gym.compact and light turbo fan is perfect for portable to everywhere\"},{\"attr_name\":\"Multi-use and Anti-Lost\",\"attr_value\":\"Whether handheld,hanging on your wrist,put on desk or hang on any backpack, portable fan can meet your different needs.the personal fan with a lanyard for anti-lost.and it takes small footprint to put your purse,makeup bag,backpack,luggage.it is very convenient for outdoor or travel.\"},{\"attr_name\":\"Gift Summer Essentials\",\"attr_value\":\"The portable handheld fan is suitable as birthday,anniversary,Thanksgivings,Christmas,outdoor party gifts for women, men,moms,kids, family, and friends. if you have any quality problem,please contact us to get 1 year wrranty .\"}]",
